title: Cog - Just Visiting (Parts 1 and 2)
description:
Cog is an Australian progressive rock band that formed in 1998. 

Their debut album The New Normal was nominated for Triple J&#039;s 2005 J Award. 

The band&#039;s music draws influences from Tool, Isis, Nina Simone, Bob Marley, Leftfield, and Helmet.
